## ⚙️ LangGraph State Schema

```python
from langgraph.graph import StateGraph, END
from typing import TypedDict, Annotated, List
import operator

class AgentState(TypedDict):
    # Core
    goal: str
    scratchpad: Annotated[List[str], operator.add]   # append-only log
    messages: Annotated[List[dict], operator.add]

    # Planning
    plan: List[str]          # ordered sub-tasks
    current_step: int
    strategy: str            # "decompose" | "hypothesis" | "ooda" | "heuristic"

    # Memory
    working_memory: dict
    episodic_hits: List[dict]  # retrieved past runs
    retrieved_docs: List[str]

    # Execution
    tool_results: Annotated[List[dict], operator.add]
    parallel_tasks: List[str]

    # Control
    reflection_score: float    # 0.0–1.0 from critic node
    retry_count: int
    human_approval_needed: bool
    final_answer: str
    confidence: float
    error: str
```

