## 🧩 What Makes It "Unpredictable"

| Mechanism | How it creates variability |
|---|---|
| **Strategy router** | 5 different reasoning loops chosen per goal type |
| **Temperature 0.7** | Non-deterministic LLM outputs on each run |
| **Reflection revision** | Critic rewrites the plan mid-execution |
| **Parallel fanout** | Sub-agents explore branches simultaneously |
| **Episodic memory** | Past failures alter current strategy choices |
| **OODA loop** | Real-time tool results change next actions dynamically |
| **Human interrupts** | Introduces external signals mid-graph |

This gives you a production-grade, self-adapting agent that reasons differently every run while staying bounded by hard safety stops.
